window = PyQt5.QtWidgets.QWidget()
with mock.patch.object(app, 'runDialog', return_value=1):
    with mock.patch.object(PyQt5.QtWidgets.QFileDialog, 'selectedFiles',
        return_value=['mw4/test/test.txt']):
        full, short, ext = app.saveFile(window=window, title='title',
            folder='.', filterSet='*.*')
    assert short == 'test'
    assert ext == '.txt'
